For each unique CASE_ID, calculate the total paid amount across all claims (CA_UNIVERSE_T.HDR_PD_AMT) and insert a new record into CA_FINANCIAL_TERMS_T:
•	RXA Total Paid Amount: Populate FIN_CUST_AMT_A with the SUM(HDR_PD_AMT).
•	RXA Total Correct Amount: Populate INFORMAL_AMT with the SUM(HDR_PD_AMT).
•	OMIG/RXA Final Questioned Cost: Populate RECOUP_AMT with 0.00.
•	Final Questioned Cost: Populate TOTAL_PAID_AMT with 0.00.
•	Balanced Questioned Cost: Populate OUTSTAND_AMT with 0.00.
